These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, soy-milk
6 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, backgammon, snooker, chess, billiard
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person playing go is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
6. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person playing chess is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee  | iced-tea    | lemonade  | cola      | milk    |
| Game      | go  | billiard | chess | mah-jongg | snooker | backgammon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: motorbike, train, skateboard, car, taxi, jet-ski
6 different pets are kept: dog, goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is the owner of the mouse##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the train##1
9. the person driving the motorbike is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Transport   | motorbike   | taxi | train | jet-ski | car     | skateboard  |
| Pet           | goldfish | goat    | dog      | mouse  | guinea-pig | lizard |

