.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, indie, punk, soul
City: miami, rome, edinburgh, boston, venice, colone
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of soul##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of country is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
5. the fan of punk is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
6. the fan of punk is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
7. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to edinburgh is the fan of indie##1
9. the fan of country is the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | soul   | punk      | classical | blues  | country   |
| City   | edinburgh | colone | miami | rome   | venice | boston |

