.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: country, disco, dubstep, folk, indie, pop
There are 6 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, fanta, mirinda, juice, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of country##1
5. the person drinking juice is the fan of pop##1
6. the fan of disco is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
8. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
9. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | dubstep    | country | indie     | disco   | folk     |
| Beverage   | juice | 7up | hot-chocolate | fanta | mirinda | sprite |

