.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-7::.
6 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, guinea-pig, horse, snake, turtle
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bluemaster, baccarat, alhambra, game, tiparillo
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the game-smoker is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the owner of the horse is the tiparillo-smoker##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is the baccarat-smoker##1
7. the prince-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
8. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Pet         | dog       | turtle     | horse | guinea-pig | snake | chinchilla |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | game | tiparillo | baccarat     | prince  | alhambra       |

