.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: ambient, funk, hip-hop, punk, reggae, salsa
There are 6 different favourite colors: ivory, grey, blood-red, green, light-blue, apricot
1. the fan of hip-hop is the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who likes apricot is the fan of punk##1
3. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
5. the person who likes grey is the fan of salsa##1
6. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
8. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | ambient  | reggae     | hip-hop    | funk  | punk          |
| Color         | grey  | ivory | blood-red | light-blue | green | apricot |

