.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, cranberry, kiwi, onion, peach, peas
6 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, bridge, monopoly, whist, backgammon
1. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
3. the person playing canasta is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person playing whist##1
5. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
7. the person eating peas is the person playing scrabble##1
8. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
9. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | cranberry | peas   | peach  | kiwi    | onion  | broccoli |
| Game   | canasta   | scrabble | backgammon | whist | bridge | monopoly |

