The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: zombie, scientific, family, crime, animation, fantasy
The people have 6 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, librarian, manager, pilot, writer
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
