4. the librarian is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the fisherman is on the far right##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is the manager##1
8. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
9. the pilot is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
