.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-13::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: september, april, february, june, january, july
The people use 6 different means of transport: car, motorbike, roller, scooter, tram, trike
1. the person who's birthday is in june is the person driving the roller##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
8. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
9. the person who's birthday is in july is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |       3        |     4     |     5     |   6    |
| Birthday         | february | april | january | june | september    | july |
| Transport   | car   | tram      | scooter        | roller    | motorbike | trike  |

