.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3     |       4       |       5       |    6     |
| Flower   | marigold | bellflower | dahlia  | aconite | balloon-flower       | daisy   |
| Sport   | parkour | lacrosse     | handball | skiing        | skateboarding | swimming |

