There are 6 different favourite colors: fuchsia, pink, emerald, chestnut, white, grey
1. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes white##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
6. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes white##1
7. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
8. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
9. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | salsa     | rock       | house  | metal | country    |
| Color     | grey  | fuchsia | pink | chestnut | white  | emerald |

 